name: iPhone 3G Hard Case III
description:
Safeguard the iPhone 3 from dings and scratches with this rugged & durable hard plastic case (with a polished finish). It snaps onto devices and gives easy access to all controls.

    * Fits iPhone 3G, 3Gs
    * Snaps snugly into place
    * Hard polished plastic
    * Easy access to all controls
